    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/11452883c3fd29a80c99fd8684403c2a.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/11452883c3fd29a80c99fd8684403c2a.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/11452883c3fd29a80c99fd8684403c2a.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>凭借大量的动作和肾上腺素，我们只为您带来街机足球最激动人心的部分！<br>使用我们独有的游戏，可选择单人游戏模式或本地多人游戏。 您甚至可以使用 Remote Play Together 来分享游戏！<br>最多 4 名玩家可以在任何游戏模式中享受竞争或合作的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/f622d8ea8ea563655fbb96a4bf4642ed.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/f622d8ea8ea563655fbb96a4bf4642ed.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/f622d8ea8ea563655fbb96a4bf4642ed.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >播放模式:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/dab3e3e103a5a5c074cb7bb5d01fd8cb.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/dab3e3e103a5a5c074cb7bb5d01fd8cb.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/dab3e3e103a5a5c074cb7bb5d01fd8cb.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ol><li> 友谊赛和点球大战<br></li><li> 比赛 - 参加最重要的比赛！<br></li><li> 职业模式！ - 从头开始​​创建你的团队并带领它走向辉煌！<br></li><li> 主题活动 - 具有惊人角色的疯狂游戏模式。<br></li><li> 派对比赛 - 与朋友和家人一起玩！</li></ol><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可参加的比赛：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/3199bdee4d3964a0d8ea58db6d7931db.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/3199bdee4d3964a0d8ea58db6d7931db.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/3199bdee4d3964a0d8ea58db6d7931db.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Charrua 锦标赛和 Charrua A 和 B 联赛<br></li><li> 欧洲、美洲和亚洲杯<br></li><li> 奥林查鲁亚杯（男性和女性）<br></li><li> 全球杯（男女）<br></li><li> 1930 年全球杯（以复古风格唤起第一个国际杯）<br></li><li> 美国联赛（男性和女性）<br></li><li> 欧洲联赛和自由杯</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征：</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/16b3ae88c575f45ffa069fb6b5aeea76.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/16b3ae88c575f45ffa069fb6b5aeea76.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/16b3ae88c575f45ffa069fb6b5aeea76.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 休闲玩家的简化控制，可以连接您选择的无线兼容控制器。<br></li><li> 易于学习和享受，具有干净且具有挑战性的游戏玩法。<br></li><li> 可配置的辅助模式，以帮助您执行您喜欢的操作或禁用它以增加挑战。<br></li><li> 复古风格的 3D 艺术，类似于旧游戏并唤起怀旧之情。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/91b6911346ec757457173951f060a2cf.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/91b6911346ec757457173951f060a2cf.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/91b6911346ec757457173951f060a2cf.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 派对模式：在不同的游戏模式中与您的朋友一起玩。<br></li><li> 犯规、任意球、黄牌和红牌、伤病和点球！<br></li><li> 女子、男子和混合足球。<br></li><li> 深度游戏：短传、长传、定向射门、控制射门或吊球射门、球员技巧等等。<br></li><li> 大量动画（过顶踢、蝎子踢、剪刀踢、跳水头球等）<br></li><li> 挑战人工智能。游戏风格迥异的球队（例如，来自意大利的 Catenaccio 或像巴西这样的 Tiki-taka）。<br></li><li> 管理团队组建和战略、球员变化等等。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/38369c22777e56eda58069a8e9f709f0.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/38369c22777e56eda58069a8e9f709f0.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/38369c22777e56eda58069a8e9f709f0.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>无论您是不是足球迷，这款游戏都能让您玩上几个小时！<br>你有成为冠军的条件吗？<br><br>随时发布或与我们联系，提出您的建议和想法。我们一直在关注玩家的反馈，以使 Charrua Soccer 成为世界上最好的复古足球游戏！",
